      <title>巴基斯坦有“可信证据”将印度特工与杀害巴基斯坦公民联系起来</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pakistan-has-credible-evidence-link-indian-agents-killings-pakistani-citizens-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦周四表示，有“可靠证据”表明印度特工与在巴基斯坦境内杀害两名巴基斯坦公民有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/pakistan-has-credible-evidence-link-indian-agents-killings-pakistani-citizens-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:53:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>主教获教宗批准在中国祝圣，中美关系明显解冻</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/bishop-approved-by-pope-ordained-china-apparent-thaw-relations-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梵蒂冈表示，周四，由教皇方济各任命的一位主教在中国的一个教区就任，由于政府支持的主教在未经教皇许可的情况下被任命，由此引发的摩擦导致两国关系明显解冻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/bishop-approved-by-pope-ordained-china-apparent-thaw-relations-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:50:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国志愿者取代因炮火逃离以色列农场的工人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/foreign-volunteers-replace-workers-who-fled-israeli-farms-under-fire-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·兰兹曼并没有在加勒比海的阳光下舒展身体，而是在以色列度假，在巴勒斯坦火箭弹的攻击范围内无偿采摘西红柿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/foreign-volunteers-replace-workers-who-fled-israeli-farms-under-fire-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和越南将签署海岸警卫队协议，此举可能会激怒中国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-sign-coastguard-deal-risking-chinas-ire-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，菲律宾和越南将同意在菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯下周访问河内期间加强海岸警卫队合作，此举可能会激怒中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-sign-coastguard-deal-risking-chinas-ire-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:42:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸前领导人昂山素季的软禁地点价值至少9000万美元——法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-ex-leader-suu-kyis-house-arrest-site-worth-least-90mln-court-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，一位消息人士称，军方管理的缅甸一家法院已将拍卖前领导人、民主偶像昂山素季被软禁 15 年的别墅，起拍价为 3,150 亿缅币（合 9,000 万美元）。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-ex-leader-suu-kyis-house-arrest-site-worth-least-90mln-court-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:28:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国谴责美国在台海的“挑衅”并承诺进一步演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-slams-us-provocation-taiwan-strait-pledges-further-drills-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，美国海军自台湾总统和议会选举以来第一艘军舰驶过敏感的台湾海峡后，中国批评美国制造“麻烦和挑衅”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-slams-us-provocation-taiwan-strait-pledges-further-drills-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台央行纪要：若高通胀持续，不排除进一步收紧政策</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-central-bank-minutes-cant-rule-out-more-tightening-if-high-inflation-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四公布的上次董事会会议纪要显示，台湾央行的一些董事会成员指出了对通胀上升的“持续”担忧，并表示，如果通胀持续高位，不排除进一步收紧货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-central-bank-minutes-cant-rule-out-more-tightening-if-high-inflation-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:05:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国议员街头遇袭 袭击者被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-member-parliament-attacked-yonhap-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国执政党人民党称，周四，一名身份不明的袭击者用物体击中一名议员的头部，要求她住院治疗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-member-parliament-attacked-yonhap-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 08:47:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警告社交媒体上吃油炸牙签的风潮</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-warns-against-social-media-trend-eating-fried-toothpicks-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国食品部发出健康警告，敦促人们不要吃由淀粉制成的形状类似炸薯条的油炸牙签，此前这种做法在社交媒体帖子中疯传。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-warns-against-social-media-trend-eating-fried-toothpicks-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 07:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国提前降息的希望减弱，亚洲外汇空头势头增强</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-gain-momentum-hopes-early-us-rate-cuts-wane-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透调查显示，随着交易员调整对美联储提前降息的押注，对多种亚洲新兴货币的看跌押注增加，推动投资者转向避险美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-gain-momentum-hopes-early-us-rate-cuts-wane-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 07:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
